text: 20 minute wait. Easier just to a normal branch. No teas/coffees even available.  What's the point ?

Absolutely amazing staff here. Found a seat and was immediately approached by the staff to ask what drink I fancied.

Coffee and tea came with Swiss bake cookies which was just delightful. Also, Free Wifi

Absolutely amazing service by the lovely wait staff! I was never in shortage of delicious fusionberry cookies and cappuccino. This branch will definitely be where I do my banking activities in the future.

Another DBS Treasure lounge.... this is one of the larger lounges but the quality needs to be upgraded. UOB and OCBC are definitely ahead in this area.

The plus point is this lounge in open on weekends! Free drinks, anyone?!
This place is great! They have fast transactions and they supported us immediately!
